In Dockerfile

# Use an official PHP image with Apache pre-installed
FROM php:8.1-apache

# Copy your project files into the container's web root
COPY ./your-php-app /var/www/html/

# Expose the port Apache is running on
EXPOSE 80


Build docker image
docker build -t my-php-app .

Run image
docker run -d -p 8080:80 my-php-app

View your application at http://localhost:8080
